{"id":"ca1ed593-3a3c-491c-a11d-cac66a304115","name":"Maleficent | Sleeping Beauty’s Story","description":"<p>𝐄𝐯𝐞𝐫𝐲 𝐬𝐭𝐨𝐫𝐲 𝐧𝐞𝐞𝐝𝐬 𝐚 𝐯𝐢𝐥𝐥𝐚𝐢𝐧. 𝐘𝐨𝐮 𝐬𝐡𝐨𝐮𝐥𝐝 𝐛𝐞 𝐠𝐫𝐚𝐭𝐞𝐟𝐮𝐥 𝐭𝐡𝐚𝐭 𝐢𝐭'𝐬 𝐦𝐞.</p><p>𝐅𝐨𝐫 𝐭𝐡𝐞𝐲 𝐜𝐚𝐥𝐥𝐞𝐝 𝐦𝐞 𝐞𝐯𝐢𝐥, 𝐛𝐮𝐭 𝐨𝐧𝐥𝐲 𝐛𝐞𝐜𝐚𝐮𝐬𝐞 𝐈 𝐫𝐞𝐟𝐮𝐬𝐞𝐝 𝐭𝐨 𝐛𝐨𝐰.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/-YEITTJnKjGTe3ZP4WZy2.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p>𝒪𝓃𝒸𝑒 𝓊𝓅𝑜𝓃 𝒶 𝓉𝒾𝓂𝑒, there was a princess who thought the world would give her happily ever after.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 255, 0);\">𝓗𝓸𝔀 𝓺𝓾𝓪𝓲𝓷𝓽.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/5RR2aG35E3Ktt4jnnjK2R.webp\" style=\"width: 440px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p>You've been gone for so long - the princess of the northern reaches of Eldralore, cursed to fall into a sleep which you shall never awaken. Until true love's kiss, that is, or so they say. And while you slept, your kingdom fell into the hands of another - even your fiancee, the prince of another kingdom, forgot you completely.</p><p>No one ever came to save you.</p><p>So why, oh, why, did you wake from your dreams after all - to the kiss of the very fae who cursed you to begin with? Is it possibly the truth, that he's your true love after all?</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/5RR2aG35E3Ktt4jnnjK2R.webp\" style=\"width: 433px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/AsZ_zKNtjL02wypg2p62P.webp\" style=\"width: 377px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 255, 0);\">♫</span> Soundtrack: <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8waJ7W3QcJc\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(27, 212, 0);\">Once Upon a Dream</span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/-YEITTJnKjGTe3ZP4WZy2.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/Gzq6W_npMHFjkIXTYUhct.webp\" style=\"width: 532px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">This is part of the <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/search?mode=all&amp;sort=popular&amp;custom_tags=twistedtalesseries&amp;page=1\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(154, 255, 98);\">Twisted Tales collaboration</span></a> between myself and some other talented writers in the <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/external-link?to=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2Fa4C5c2dPEV\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(209, 98, 255);\">TearWave Systems server</span></a>. This is based off of Cinderella! I'd highly recommend checking out the others in the series -</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/e219eb0b-5227-4d2f-a262-118e90f08575_character-snow-whites-story-king-malachi-step-dad\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 37, 37);\">⋆｡°✩ King Malachi - Snow White's Story, by Violetzz ✩°｡⋆</span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(71, 255, 183);\">⋆｡°✩ </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/e5a94cfe-324e-4159-8c7a-ad391ed73c0c_character-titanius-the-summer-king-a-midsummer-nights-dream\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(217, 255, 71);\">Titanius</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(71, 255, 183);\"> and </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/8f86d7dc-439e-4b40-957c-435ad7e7b94c_character-king-oberon-twisted-tales-series\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(71, 199, 255);\">Oberon</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(71, 255, 183);\"> (A Midsummer Night's Dream), by SparrowShark and RisenQueen ✩°｡⋆</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/9b46f9bf-cc6e-4dce-9893-1855b0e8c610_character-puss-in-boots\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 176","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"87acebe3-b89f-4142-988c-b327533cd99e_9be8c061-44da-4496-ab08-bfd707e16165.webp","creator":"sparrowshark","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🏰 Historical","🦹‍♂️ Villain","🔮 Magical","⛓️ Dominant","🕊🗡 Dead Dove","👩 FemPov"],"chats":2818,"messages":54390,"created_at":"2024-11-30T14:55:10.124491+00:00"}